plot: An accident in the Candy Kingdom which Finn and Jake cause is blamed on the Duke of Nuts. Finn and Jake, however, find admitting the truth to be harder and harder as time passes.

In "The Duke", Finn and Jake accidentally turns Princess Bubblegum green and bald, and faces a moral quandary - admit to the crime or allow the Duke of Nuts to take the fall. In "Donny", Finn and Jake try to reform a bullying ogre, but realize that their good deed has unexpected consequences.—unknown
